data.description: Nestled on a generous corner lot, this inviting cottage is an ideal choice for those embarking on homeownership. Prepare to be amazed by the spacious backyard, featuring an above-ground pool and deck. The one-car detached garage not only provides ample storage but also offers the option of transforming into an enclosed patio. Conveniently situated near major thoroughfares, this home provides easy access to nearby shopping centers and eateries. Additionally, it's just minutes away from the expressway, facilitating a seamless commute to Chicago and nearby malls. Experience the perfect blend of comfort and accessibility in this charming abode.
